{"tid":2201664,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有市民月初已做過檢測　但擔心受感染決定再檢測一次","createTime":"2020-09-14T03:32:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-14T06:08:36.000Z","uid":5312,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"9b8940a2dd68cd541512bf8d2f54a36abc6cd522","tid":2201664,"uid":5312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T03:32:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1549468_1_L_20200914111028.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1549468_1_L_20200914111028.jpg&h=e2c8a043&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"small\">將軍澳官立小學的檢測中心，早上人流不算多，1小時內約有10人前往接受採樣。（任浩鋒攝）</span><br />\n<br />\n普及社區檢測計劃最後一日，有57間檢測中心朝8晚8繼續運作為市民進行檢測採樣。其中在將軍澳官立小學的檢測中心，早上人流不算多，1小時內約有10人前往接受採樣，當中不少人並無預約登記。<br />\n<br />\n有市民說，為了避開早前採樣的人潮而選擇今天最後一日才做檢測，接受採樣為求安心。<br />\n<br />\n有家庭主婦表示，身邊及住所附近都無人確診，就是否做檢測思考了數天，考慮到有家人在安老院，希望得出陰性病毒測試結果後，日後可以去探望，因此決定接受採樣。<br />\n<br />\n至於在麥花臣場館的檢測中心，早上人流亦不算多，有市民趁最後一天到場，表示之前都要上班，趁今日放假來做檢測，她形容檢測過程快，5分鐘內已完成。亦有市民已第二次接受採樣，他表示9月2日已接受了一次檢測，因為擔心自己會受感染，再加上檢測中心在住所附近，於是在計劃結束前，再做多一次。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1549468-20200914.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1549468-20200914.htm&d=L%2FLAiDqbkajbTQHtoaAw8OSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=2aa36a58\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1549468-20200914.htm&h=98a88074\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1549468-20200914.htm</a>"},{"pid":"35c6b0f40cc007444349c1cbaafab6d91a49e665","tid":2201664,"uid":5312,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T03:33:21.000Z","msg":"永續檢測<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e6fe4c77f79095b841db1870b61b1b9fe35fcaa","tid":2201664,"uid":135867,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T03:33:32.000Z","msg":"咁其實要每六個鐘測一次"},{"pid":"762a15f94ae92cbd0f1d3b59ffe48e20734be70b","tid":2201664,"uid":21545,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T03:33:34.000Z","msg":"咁中意畀人抽插<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b028c91b69984717143dffb57c242ab5d4822fd","tid":2201664,"uid":226622,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T03:34:43.000Z","msg":"月初做完覺醒左性辟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"522ee2899f745c9d6f6b1c0fceeb3ec828a263e3","tid":2201664,"uid":343754,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T03:36:56.000Z","msg":"之前做過一次再做有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb86072a6bcfdfec83b824dc58c9c1c79a2a19ff","tid":2201664,"uid":37757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T03:41:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"afd907dfe118589e404f601122f2876294b8565a","tid":2201664,"uid":5312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"522ee2899f745c9d6f6b1c0fceeb3ec828a263e3","tid":2201664,"uid":343754,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T03:36:56.000Z","msg":"之前做過一次再做有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T03:41:34.000Z","msg":"問題係港共吹奏到做咗檢測之後<br />\n就好似唔會再疫情咁<br />\n根本成個所謂檢測計劃都係想營造出港共幫香港"},{"pid":"b9cdfa07a8a747ae983ae530669f5c2038be9750","tid":2201664,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T03:42:47.000Z","msg":"你日日都有機會感染架啦﹐你唔好日日做"},{"pid":"58c2031ca7d5a01244c09abc163ee3d3354c536e","tid":2201664,"uid":81052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T03:43:05.000Z","msg":"我唔使染都知14日前冇感染"},{"pid":"a5042de8cd1fdb838fd0f377f950d1802ac2e55f","tid":2201664,"uid":202876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco